# Project: Nuxt 3 + TailwindCSS + TypeScript

## Stack overview

- Framework: Nuxt 3
- Styling: TailwindCSS + project CSS variables
- Language: TypeScript
- Component API: Vue 3 Composition API (`<script setup>`)

## Component file structure

Every `.vue` file must follow this order:

1. `<script setup lang="ts">`
2. `<template>`
3. `<style scoped lang="postcss">`
   Use TailwindCSS in `<template>`, ensure custom CSS variables where needed. Style section must always be last.

